         <abstract id="aspace_f5310141e18f09e482b9442216de2de8">The Ken White Collection documents the graphic design career of Ken White from 1964 to 1985 through examples of publications and ephemera he designed for specific clients. White worked for a variety of clients, including IBM, <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
               <part>Better Homes and Gardens</part>
            </title>, and the Phoenix Art Museum.</abstract>
